{
  "id": "5de65f2e1a9a6400175ec9b3",
  "title": "CSSで条件分岐と変数と計算を使う",
  "created": 1575378736,
  "updated": 1585213636,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5de65f2e1a9a6400175ec9b3",
      "text": "CSSで条件分岐と変数と計算を使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378736,
      "updated": 1575378864
    },
    {
      "id": "5de65fb2aff09e00007126dc",
      "text": " [メディアクエリ]で条件分岐ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378866,
      "updated": 1576815586
    },
    {
      "id": "5de6610aaff09e00007126f1",
      "text": " \t[メディアクエリの使用 - CSS: カスケーディングスタイルシート | MDN https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379211,
      "updated": 1575379362
    },
    {
      "id": "5de6610baff09e00007126f2",
      "text": " \t印刷画面と通常画面を切り替えるものってイメージでいた(メディアっていうし)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379212,
      "updated": 1575379362
    },
    {
      "id": "5de6611daff09e00007126f3",
      "text": " \tしかし画面サイズを条件式に加えることができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379229,
      "updated": 1575379362
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66128aff09e00007126f4",
      "text": " [カスタムプロパティ]で変数を作れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379241,
      "updated": 1576815584
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66160aff09e00007126f5",
      "text": " \t[CSS カスタムプロパティ (変数) の使用 - CSS: カスケーディングスタイルシート | MDN https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Using_CSS_custom_properties]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379296,
      "updated": 1575379362
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660daaff09e00007126f0",
      "text": "  :root 擬似クラスがグローバルスコープがわりに使える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379162,
      "updated": 1575379362
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66183aff09e00007126f6",
      "text": "\tcalc()で計算できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379331,
      "updated": 1575379366
    },
    {
      "id": "5de661a6aff09e00007126f7",
      "text": "\t\t[calc() - CSS: カスケーディングスタイルシート | MDN https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/calc]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379366,
      "updated": 1575379366
    },
    {
      "id": "5de661a7aff09e00007126f8",
      "text": "\tJSで取得できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379368,
      "updated": 1585213132
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c6eb4aff09e0000795dec",
      "text": "\t\t`getComputedStyle(document.body).getPropertyValue(\"--toolbar-height\")`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213109,
      "updated": 1585213112
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c707baff09e000071009f",
      "text": "\t\tstringなので単位を仮定したらこんな感じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213563,
      "updated": 1585213635
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c6ea4aff09e0000c65ced",
      "text": "\t\tcode:ts",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213095,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7073aff09e0000710099",
      "text": "\t\t const toolbarHeight = parseInt(",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213556,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7074aff09e000071009a",
      "text": "       getComputedStyle(document.body)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213556,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7074aff09e000071009b",
      "text": "         .getPropertyValue(\"--toolbar-height\")",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213556,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7074aff09e000071009c",
      "text": "         .trim()",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213556,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7074aff09e000071009d",
      "text": "     );",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213556,
      "updated": 1585213556
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7c7076aff09e000071009e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585213558,
      "updated": 1585213558
    },
    {
      "id": "5de6fe78aff09e000058ec09",
      "text": "横幅が狭い時にツールバーの高さを縮めてボタンも小さくするcss",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575419513,
      "updated": 1575419573
    },
    {
      "id": "5de65f49aff09e00007126d7",
      "text": "code:css",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378761,
      "updated": 1575378764
    },
    {
      "id": "5de65f36aff09e00007126d4",
      "text": " :root {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378742,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126dd",
      "text": "   --toolbar-height: 60px;",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126de",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126df",
      "text": " @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e0",
      "text": "   :root {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e1",
      "text": "     --toolbar-height: 36px;",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e2",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e3",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e4",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378952
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e5",
      "text": " #toolbar {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e6",
      "text": "   height: var(--toolbar-height);",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378949
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126e7",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378954
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660c8aff09e00007126eb",
      "text": " #toolbar svg {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379144,
      "updated": 1575379145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660c9aff09e00007126ec",
      "text": "   height: calc(var(--toolbar-height) * 0.8);",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379145,
      "updated": 1575379145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660c9aff09e00007126ed",
      "text": "   margin: calc(var(--toolbar-height) * 0.1) 0 calc(var(--toolbar-height) * 0.1) 0;",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379145,
      "updated": 1575379145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660c9aff09e00007126ee",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379145,
      "updated": 1575379145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de660c9aff09e00007126ef",
      "text": "最近の[CSS]は便利！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379145,
      "updated": 1575380376
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66291aff09e00007126f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379602,
      "updated": 1575379602
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66292aff09e00007126fa",
      "text": "code:css",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379602,
      "updated": 1575379605
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66295aff09e00007126fb",
      "text": " /* ボタン7つを３グループに分けるスペーサー */",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379605,
      "updated": 1575379628
    },
    {
      "id": "5de662abaff09e00007126ff",
      "text": " #toolbar span.spacer {",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379628,
      "updated": 1575379636
    },
    {
      "id": "5de662abaff09e0000712700",
      "text": "   margin-left: calc((100vw - var(--button-size) * 7) / 2);",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379628,
      "updated": 1575379636
    },
    {
      "id": "5de662abaff09e0000712701",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575379628,
      "updated": 1575379636
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66000aff09e00007126ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575378945,
      "updated": 1575378945
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66ab8aff09e0000144b59",
      "text": "余談",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575381688,
      "updated": 1575381690
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66abaaff09e0000144b5b",
      "text": "\tクラス名にパターンマッチもできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575381690,
      "updated": 1575381698
    },
    {
      "id": "5de66ac2aff09e0000144b5c",
      "text": "\t\t[Attribute selectors - CSS: Cascading Style Sheets | MDN https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors?fbclid=IwAR0QOFAM0qUYu8eWeDTveDUrH3fbEhYRh3ocF-6M-z61wrfdELQitgcOdfs]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575381698,
      "updated": 1575381699
    },
